cs.DC, cs.MS, cs.NA, cs.PF, cs.SE

Reasoning: 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is the most likely category, as the paper deals with load balancing in parallel computing using MPI+X.
- cs.MS (Mathematical Software) is also likely, as the paper proposes a novel approach for load balancing in adaptive mesh refinement codes, which involves mathematical modeling and analysis.
- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) is another possible category, as the paper deals with numerical simulations using a high order ADER-DG scheme.
- cs.PF (Performance) is also possible, as the paper aims to improve the performance of parallel adaptive mesh refinement codes by exploiting idle time.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is less likely, but still possible, as the paper proposes a new approach for load balancing in software development.
